summary:
It would be good for Europe if the greatness that the continent has spawned is really realized: Europe is much more than a market and a single currency, it is the area where both misery took place as where great artistic, literary, social & intellectual and religious movements did arise. Europe is an idea and a project.

Feeling Europe Foundation participated in 'The Sound of Europe' international conference and fosters and guides European achievements, aiming to improve living conditions as well as human condition. The desk:

- brings European values and affairs in front;
- takes position as nexus between citizens and institutions;
- delivers resonance, builds, informs and connects;
- is doing research.

Knowledge was obtained through formal and informal teachings, autodidactism, and instruction and guidance from experts and community. 

In order to keep up to date and to increase knowledge, following centres are engaged: the Nexus Institute, Center for European Policy Studies (CEPS), Bruegel, Dutch Chapter of the European Movement International, Dutch Society for International Affairs, the Royal Dutch Economic Association, Caux Round Table for Moral Capitalism, Council for Inclusive Capitalism (ally), Odyssey, Convention of Independent Financial Advisors (CIFA), and member Gobal Blockchain Business Council (GBCC).
